title: Are You UnF*ck Your Brain’s Next Marketing Director?
itunes:title: Are You UnF*ck Your Brain’s Next Marketing Director?
description: UnF*ck Your Brain is hiring a Marketing Director! Are you a great writer who’s obsessed with developing content strategy, geeking out on analytics, overseeing marketing initiatives, and getting life-changing coaching tools into the hands of as many people as possible? If all that sounds like a dream, you may be our next Marketing Director. Listen to this episode to learn more about the position, or head straight to unfuckyourbrain.com/hiring for details on how to apply!
